'''耳尺蛾屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Ramobia'''''}}）是[[尺蛾科|尺蛾科]]之下的一個[[屬_(生物)|屬]]，舊屬[[Alcis|Alcis]]屬<ref name=Sato2002>{{cite journal |author={{aut|Sato, Rikio}} |authorlink=佐藤力夫 |year=2002 |title=Two new species and two new subspecies of the ''Boarmiini'' from Taiwan, with notes on ''Alcis anmashanensis'' Sato (Geometridae: Ennominae). |journal=''Transactions of the Lepidopterological Society of Japan'' |volume=53 |issue=3 |pages=pp.141-149 |url=http://ci.nii.ac.jp/naid/110007630967/en |language=en |access-date=2013-03-24 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304231302/http://ci.nii.ac.jp/naid/110007630967/en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。現時本屬有四個物種，在[[日本|日本]]、[[台灣|台灣]]<ref name=Sato2002 />及[[泰國|泰國]]<ref name=Sato2005>{{cite journal |author={{aut|Sato, R.}} |authorlink=佐藤力夫 |year=2005 |title=Records of the ''Boarmiini'' (Geometridae: Ennominae) from Thailand IV |journal=''Transactions of the Lepidopterological Society of Japan'' |volume=56 |issue=1 |pages=pp.63-72 |url=http://ci.nii.ac.jp/naid/110007138325/en |language=en |access-date=2013-03-24 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305002652/http://ci.nii.ac.jp/naid/110007138325/en |dead-url=no }}</ref>皆有發現，當中在台灣發現的還是特有品種<ref name=TaiBNET>{{TaiBNET| zh=鞍馬山耳尺蛾 | id=345228 | binomial=Ramobia anmashana | authority=Sato, 2002 |authoritylink=佐藤力夫 | var= | accessdate=2013-01-24}}</ref>。

